      "annotation_type": "source_note",
      "annotation_text": "Grading via CTCAE, Version 5.0. As part of AE collection, monitor vital signs and perform standard laboratory tests (hematology, chemistry, urinalysis, and pregnancy testing) at the same frequency as during the study treatment period. See Section 10.3 for AE grading for lab investigations. All laboratory tests during the continued access period will be performed in the local laboratories only.",
