      "annotation_text": "In the event of hypersensitivity, blood samples will be collected for PK, IG, and exploratory hypersensitivity analyses at the following time points, as close as possible to: (i) the onset of the hypersensitivity, (ii) the resolution of the hypersensitivity, and (iii) 30 (+/-3) days following the hypersensitivity.",
